1.15s steps(1) infinite\"></span></a><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-0.5 md:flex\"><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/projects\">Projects</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/articles\">Articles</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/tours\">Tours</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"true\" href=\"/about\">About</a></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a aria-label=\"mkdir\" class=\"glass-pill mono h-10 shrink-0 gap-1.5 px-2.5 text-[13px] font-medium sm:px-3.5\" style=\"color:var(--ink)\" href=\"/mkdir\"><svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\"><polyline points=\"4 17 10 11 4 5\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"19\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"19\"></line></svg><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\"><span style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\"></span>mkdir</span></a><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Switch to dark theme\" class=\"glass-icon-btn flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"md:hidden\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-nav-panel\" class=\"glass-icon-btn flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></nav></div></div><!--$?--><template id=\"B:0\"></template><main class=\"relative z-[3] mx-auto w-full max-w-[820px] px-[22px] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\"></main><!--/$--><footer class=\"relative z-[3] flex justify-center px-[22px] pt-[30px] pb-11\"><div class=\"flex w-full max-w-[1180px] flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-[18px] sm:px-[22px]\" style=\"border-radius:20px;background:var(--glass-bg);background-image:var(--glass-tint);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur)) saturate(180%);border:1px solid var(--glass-brd);box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 var(--glass-hi)\"><span class=\"text-[13px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">© 2026 Daffa Ilham Restupratama</span><span class=\"mono text-[11px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Data · Business · Finance · Maps · Walking Tours</span></div></footer></div><script>requestAnimationFrame(function(){$RT=performance.now()});</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0a1gboz92241g.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><div hidden id=\"S:0\"><main class=\"relative z-[3] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-[820px] px-[22px]\"><header><h1 class=\"font-bold\" style=\"font-size:clamp(30px,4.5vw,50px);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.03em\">About Me</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-[16px]\" style=\"line-height:1.62;color:var(--ink-dim)\">I am an Information Systems student who enjoys connecting data, technology, business, and human-centered stories.</p></header><div class=\"mt-8\"><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">Hi, I am Daffa Ilham Restupratama, an Information Systems student at the Faculty of Computer Science, Universitas Indonesia.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">My academic and professional interests sit at the intersection of data, technology, business, and communication. I enjoy working on structured problems: understanding the context, organizing information, building systems, and communicating the result clearly.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">My current main project is a machine learning project for predicting financial distress among Indonesian public companies. Through this project, I aim to develop not only technical modeling skills, but also the ability to explain data science work in a way that is useful for business and decision-making audiences.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">Outside academic work, I have been involved in student organizations and large-scale events such as COMPFEST, Educare CSUI, and BEM Fasilkom UI. These experiences helped me develop management, communication, documentation, and cross-functional coordination skills.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">I also have a personal interest in cities, public transport, history, local food, and hidden urban stories. That interest led me to design city and walking tour concepts for places such as Jakarta, Bogor, Tangerang, and Yogyakarta.</p></div><section><h2 class=\"mt-10 mb-5 text-[22px] font-bold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.02em\">Skills</h2><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\"><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Programming Language</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used for structuring and styling responsive web pages and portfolio interfaces.\">HTML &amp; CSS<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Main programming language for data analysis, machine learning experiments, notebooks, and automation.\">Python<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">advanced</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used for statistical analysis, data exploration, and notebook-based reporting.\">R<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Academic and software engineering foundation for object-oriented programming and application logic.\">Java<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Familiar with TypeScript-based tooling through modern CMS and web development workflows.\">TypeScript<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">beginner</span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Human Language</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Native speaker. Comfortable writing professional, academic, and public-facing content.\">Indonesian<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">native</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Native speaker. Useful for local cultural contexts, community interaction, and city storytelling.\">Javanese<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">native</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Professional working proficiency for communication, documentation, research, and collaboration.\">English<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">professional</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Intermediate proficiency. Currently suitable for general communication and continued learning.\">German<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Beginner-level familiarity for basic reading and communication.\">Arabic<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">beginner</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used for web development, frontend behavior, API integration, and modern web tooling.\">JavaScript<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Database</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used as the database layer for modern web applications and CMS-backed content systems.\">PostgreSQL<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Familiar with relational database design, querying, and application integration.\">MySQL<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used for cloud-based analytics exploration and large-scale data portfolio development.\">BigQuery<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">beginner</span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Cloud</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Hands-on experience deploying and configuring cloud infrastructure for personal web projects.\">Google Cloud Platform<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Cms</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used as a headless CMS for structured content, portfolio data, blog posts, and API-driven frontend development.\">Strapi<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Familiar with traditional CMS concepts, SEO, content publishing workflows, and web administration.\">WordPress<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">beginner</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Explored Ghost for publishing workflows before moving toward a more flexible (developer-friendly) headless CMS setup.\">Ghost<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">beginner</span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Tool Software</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used for data science exploration, analysis documentation, and reproducible project reports.\">Jupyter Notbook<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">advanced</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Experienced in documents, spreadsheets, presentations, and operational coordination workflows.\">Microsoft Office &amp; Google Workspace<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">advanced</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Uses AI tools for research assistance, writing support, coding help, and workflow acceleration.\">AI-assisted productivity tools<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Design</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used for interface exploration, layout planning, and visual prototyping.\">Penpot<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">beginner</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Familiar with collaborative interface design and visual layout exploration.\">Figma<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">beginner</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Used for fast visual assets, presentation materials, and event communication design.\">Canva<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">advanced</span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"mono mb-2.5 text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Other</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Experienced in coordinating teams, structuring workstreams, and managing deliverables in student-led organizations.\">Team Management<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">intermediate</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Comfortable learning new tools, switching contexts, and handling ambiguous project requirements.\">Adaptability<span class=\"mono text-[10px] tracking-wide capitalize\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\">advanced</span></span><span class=\"chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 text-[13px]\" style=\"border-radius:999px;color:var(--ink)\" title=\"Interested in the intersection of technology, business models, financial analysis, and economic decision-making.\">Business, Finance &amp; Economics<span class=\"mono text-[10p