, Faculty of Computer Science\",\"initials\":\"UIF\",\"role\":\"Information System Fresh Graduate\",\"dateRange\":\"'21–now\",\"description\":\"Pursuing an undergraduate degree in Information Systems at the Faculty of Computer Science, Universitas Indonesia. My academic interests sit at the intersection of data, technology, business processes, and digital product development. Through coursework, organizational work, and independent projects, I have been developing a profile that combines analytical thinking, technical execution, and communication skills.\",\"startDate\":\"2021-07-01\",\"endDate\":null,\"isCurrent\":true,\"gallery\":[{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/ui_bcb906f8b8.jpg\",\"alt\":\"Foto Universitas Indonesia di sore hari.\",\"width\":1200,\"height\":675,\"caption\":\"Foto Universitas Indonesia di sore hari.\"},{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/ui_bcb906f8b8.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"width\":1200,\"height\":675,\"caption\":null},{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/ui_bcb906f8b8.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"width\":1200,\"height\":675,\"caption\":null},{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/ui_bcb906f8b8.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"width\":1200,\"height\":675,\"caption\":null},{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/ui_bcb906f8b8.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"width\":1200,\"height\":675,\"caption\":null},{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/ui_bcb906f8b8.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"width\":1200,\"height\":675,\"caption\":null}],\"logo\":{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/logo_UI_fd34e132a2.png\",\"alt\":\"Universitas Indonesia, Faculty of Computer Science\",\"width\":1396,\"height\":1526}},{\"id\":\"p0jgq6680zgvafj9u3rwbdt8\",\"category\":\"education\",\"organization\":\"SMA Negeri 1 Yogyakarta\",\"initials\":\"SNY\",\"role\":\"Student\",\"dateRange\":\"'18–'21\",\"description\":\"Completed senior high school at SMA Negeri 1 Yogyakarta. During this period, I joined Teladan Robotic Team, participated in POH Al Uswah, competed in KSN Informatics/Computer Science up to the provincial level twice, and ranked 17th overall in report-card performance across the cohort.\",\"startDate\":\"2018-07-01\",\"endDate\":\"2021-06-30\",\"isCurrent\":false,\"gallery\":[],\"logo\":{\"url\":\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/logo_teladan_e8c5f198ec.png\",\"alt\":\"Logo SMA Negeri 1 Teladan Yogyakarta\",\"width\":165,\"height\":300}}],\"organization\":[{\"id\":\"bnp2cweoeoei5figz7kiu9n5\",\"category\":\"organization\",\"organization\":\"COMPFEST\",\"initials\":\"CO\",\"role\":\"Head of Business Development & Startup Academy Staff\",\"dateRange\":\"'22–'23\",\"description\":\"Contributed to COMPFEST for two consecutive years across program and business functions. In 2022, I served as a Startup Academy staff member, supporting speaker outreach, participant liaison, speaker liaison, academy class hosting, and mentoring session operations. In 2023, I continued as Head of Business Development, managing a division responsible for revenue-generating initiatives, official merchandise, and participant souvenirs. I also initiated documentation and management structures to make the division’s workflow more organized and scalable.\",\"startDate\":\"2022-01-01\",\"endDate\":\"2023-12-31\",\"isCurrent\":false,\"gallery\":[],\"logo\":null},{\"id\":\"bkjalr4mjtleyqska8fv8b4z\",\"category\":\"organization\",\"organization\":\"Educare CSUI\",\"initials\":\"EC\",\"role\":\"Staff of Job Fair\",\"dateRange\":\"'22–'23\",\"description\":\"Served in the Job Fair division of Educare CSUI, a career-related event at the Faculty of Computer Science, Universitas Indonesia. Responsibilities included reaching out to HR representatives, collecting and curating job opportunities for the event, and supporting operational execution during the job fair sessions.\",\"startDate\":\"2022-01-01\",\"endDate\":\"2023-06-01\",\"isCurrent\":false,\"gallery\":[],\"logo\":null},{\"id\":\"kns0oy84mt4aqzlntfo0t46p\",\"category\":\"organization\",\"organization\":\"BEM Faculty of Computer Science, Universitas Indonesia\",\"initials\":\"BFC\",\"role\":\"Staff of Knowledge and Academic Affairs Division\",\"dateRange\":\"'22\",\"description\":\"Contributed to the faculty student executive board in the knowledge and academic affairs division. This experience strengthened my ability to work in structured student organizations, communicate ideas, and support programs related to academic and intellectual development.\",\"startDate\":\"2022-01-01\",\"endDate\":\"2022-12-31\",\"isCurrent\":false,\"gallery\":[],\"logo\":null},{\"id\":\"ivffli7kcl7xa2uuyl9d3b3k\",\"category\":\"organization\",\"organization\":\"Teladan Robotic Team\",\"initials\":\"TRT\",\"role\":\"Secretary / Member\",\"dateRange\":\"'18–'20\",\"description\":\"Joined the school robotics extracurricular community, gaining early exposure to technology, problem solving, teamwork, and engineering-oriented thinking.\",\"startDate\":\"2018-07-01\",\"endDate\":\"2020-06-30\",\"isCurrent\":false,\"gallery\":[],\"logo\":null}],\"others\":[]}}]\n","/about/__PAGE__":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[88265,[\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0g3rov4w115o0.js\"],\"StrapiBlocks\"]\nf:I[73708,[\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0g3rov4w115o0.js\"],\"Experiences\"]\n10:I[97367,[\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\"],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n11:\"$Sreact.suspense\"\n0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"relative z-[3] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto w-full max-w-[820px] px-[22px]\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"header\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"font-bold\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"clamp(30px,4.5vw,50px)\",\"lineHeight\":1.05,\"letterSpacing\":\"-0.03em\"},\"children\":\"About Me\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-[16px]\",\"style\":{\"lineHeight\":1.62,\"color\":\"var(--ink-dim)\"},\"children\":\"I am an Information Systems student who enjoys connecting data, technology, business, and human-centered stories.\"}]]}],null,[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Hi, I am Daffa Ilham Restupratama, an Information Systems student at the Faculty of Computer Science, Universitas Indonesia.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"My academic and professional interests sit at the intersection of data, technology, business, and communication. I enjoy working on structured problems: understanding the context, organizing information, building systems, and communicating the result clearly.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"My current main project is a machine learning project for predicting financial distress among Indonesian public companies. Through this project, I aim to develop not only technical modeling skills, but also the ability to explain data science work in a way that is useful for business and decision-making audiences.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Outside academic work, I have been involved in student organizations and large-scale events such as COMPFEST, Educare CSUI, and BEM Fasilkom UI. These experiences helped me develop management, communication, documentation, and cross-functional coordination skills.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"children\":[{\"text\":\"I also have a personal interest in cities, public transport, history, local food, and hidden urban stories. That interest led me to design city and walking tour concepts for places such as Jakarta, Bogor, Tangerang, and Yogyakarta.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 mb-5 text-[22px] font-bold\",\"style\":{\"